        overexpression, distinct <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SCF</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Pop1pand SCF</ENAMEX> Pop2pcomplexes
        were proposed to target unknown <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">substrates</ENAMEX>, but no
