          unpublished), indicated that a substantial portion of SCF
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Pop1p-Pop2pis</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT_DESC">enriched</ENAMEX> in the nucleus. To test this
          assumption, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">all five</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SCF</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Pop1p-Pop2psubunits</ENAMEX> were
          expressed as fusion <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">proteins</ENAMEX> with green fluorescent
