          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">N</ENAMEX>-terminal fusion to <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">GFP</ENAMEX> affects their localization,
          Pop1p and <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Pop2p</ENAMEX> were modified with <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">13</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">C-</ENAMEX>terminal Myc
